description: Pure node.js/javascript solution to statically complie, minify and concatenate your websites .css, .less, .coffee and .js files into user-defined bundles. Supports configurable bundle settings providing unminified, individual files ideal for development and concatenated minified .min.js and .min.css files optimal for deployment. Integrates with MVC. No .dlls, uses only text-based customizable build scripts. Self-contained, no dependencies required at run-time.
summary: Css, Less, CoffeeScript, JavaScript compiler, minifier and combiner for ASP.NET MVC websites.
